aliases: The Designate, the Supreme, Hammer Girl, Thorita, Hammerette, Thor Lass, Asgard Lass, Thoretta, Hammer Lass

marvel.description: Tarene, aware of her true nature as the Designate, a being foretold to elevate all life to greatness, sought adventure and, using Thor as a template, transformed herself into an Asgardian goddess and journeyed to Earth.

name: Thor Girl
powersText: Virtually limitless cosmic power via the use of the Chalice of Ruins and the Illumination Stone
